name: itEANz
overview:
itEANz is a SAP and IT Consulting Solutions firm. They offer a variety of services from web application, SAP services/solutions, to IT systems integration and hardware.

itEANz is a leading SAP Consulting and IT Solution Provider ,We specializes in providing solution and service to all industry verticals over 20 global clients in diverse industry .With outstanding credentials and expertise; we become one of the respected solutions provider in SAP and Web Application development. We are forward thinking organization with clear vision: providing best of breed products, superior services and reliable support to help our client leverage technology to compete, grow and succeed.

Over the years we have developed the skill sets and infrastructure to facilitate the level of services required by our clients. It is with sheer dedication, innovation, quality post production support and policy of long term business relationship with our clients that enabled us to maintain this consistent growth.
